- Plato's idea about the self is still relevant up to this day due to the advancements of technology where we can apply the idea of self against the rise of Artificial Intelligence and infer whether we can say that AI itself has a so called "soul"

- The essence of the idea about the pursuit of virtue in our daily lives is still applicable in our time, since it says a lot about our pursuit of knowledge and meaningful purpose in life which fuels our will to live.

